Interface HTMLAnchorElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Element, HTMLElement, Node
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HTMLAnchorElementImpl

    public interface HTMLAnchorElement
extends HTMLElement
    The anchor element. See the A element definition in HTML 4.01.
